summary: An ordinance relating to the improvement of 40th Ave. Southwest from Southwest 98th St. to Southwest 102nd St., and certain other streets, avenues, easements and alleys, by constructing a sanitary sewer system together with pumping stations and force mains as may be required, and otherwise improving the same, Local Improvement District No. 6299; appropriating additional funds from the Sewer Fund and amending Section 1 of Ordinance No. 92854.
